Hyena is a tool for day-to-day administration of Windows systems.

Hyena brings together all of the administrative tools from Windows
NT such as User Manager, Server Manager, and File
Manager/Explorer, and many of the MMC components from Windows
2000/2003 into a single, easy-to-use, centralized program. Hyena
arranges all system objects, such as users, servers, and groups,
in a hierarchical tree for easy and logical system administration.
